<div class="doctitle">Software Proposal &amp; Quotation</div>
<div class="docsub">Property Management Software &mdash; Real Estate &amp; Accounts Edition</div>

<table class="meta">
  <tr><td class="k">Quotation No.</td><td>QS-PM-2026-001</td><td class="k">Date</td><td>16 June 2026</td></tr>
  <tr><td class="k">Prepared For</td><td>__________________________ (Client)</td><td class="k">Valid Until</td><td>16 July 2026</td></tr>
  <tr><td class="k">Prepared By</td><td>QuickSoft &mdash; BOS Software</td><td class="k">Installation Day&nbsp;1</td><td><b>28th</b> (of the month)</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="sec">1.&nbsp; Introduction</div>
<p>Thank you for the opportunity to present <b>BOS &mdash; the Business Operating System for Property Management</b>. BOS is a complete, web-based solution that runs your entire real-estate operation and its accounting from a single platform &mdash; from leasing and rent collection to VAT-compliant invoicing and financial statements. This quotation covers the <b>Real-Estate (Property Management)</b> and <b>Accounts / Finance</b> modules only, with installation, a full one-month live trial, and training included.</p>

<div class="sec">2.&nbsp; Real Estate &mdash; Property Management</div>
<table class="feat">
  <tr><td class="g">Properties &amp; Units</td><td><ul>
    <li>Property &amp; building register; unit / flat / floor management with type &amp; status</li>
    <li>Live vacant / occupied tracking; property &amp; unit document storage</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">Parties &amp; Contacts</td><td><ul>
    <li>Landlords, Tenants, Developers, Brokers &amp; Contractors &mdash; full profiles</li>
    <li>Contact &amp; ID/trade-licence document storage with expiry tracking</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">Leasing &amp; Tenancy Contracts</td><td><ul>
    <li>Create, renew &amp; terminate tenancy contracts; rent, deposit, term &amp; schedule</li>
    <li>Full lease lifecycle; professional tenancy-contract print-out (custom designer)</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">Rent Billing &amp; Collection</td><td><ul>
    <li>Rent roll &amp; rent invoices; receipt-based rent collection</li>
    <li>Cash / bank / cheque / PDC modes; outstanding &amp; collected tracking</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">Maintenance, AMC &amp; Inspection</td><td><ul>
    <li>Maintenance / inspection scheduler &amp; calendar; work orders</li>
    <li>Contractor assignment with priority &amp; status tracking</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">Reminders &amp; Renewals</td><td><ul>
    <li>Automatic contract &amp; document expiry reminders with auto-email alerts</li>
    <li>Renewal follow-up and snooze (next reminder date &amp; time)</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">Dashboards &amp; Analytics</td><td><ul>
    <li>Occupancy %, rent roll, vacancy; ROI / yield &amp; portfolio performance</li>
    <li>Landlord payout &amp; rent-collection analytics; KPI dashboards</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">Reports</td><td><ul>
    <li>Property / unit, rent collection, outstanding, occupancy &amp; landlord statements</li></ul></td></tr>
</table>

<div class="sec">3.&nbsp; Accounts / Finance</div>
<table class="feat">
  <tr><td class="g">Invoicing &amp; Billing</td><td><ul>
    <li>Sales invoices, credit sales, quotations, proforma, delivery notes &amp; POS</li>
    <li>Multi-line entry with line &amp; document discounts</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">VAT / Tax Compliance</td><td><ul>
    <li>UAE 5% VAT (FTA-aligned); inclusive &amp; exclusive pricing; per-line tax</li>
    <li>VAT Input / Output; discount-before-tax; VAT &amp; tax reports</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">Payments, Receipts &amp; Journals</td><td><ul>
    <li>Payment &amp; receipt vouchers; journal vouchers with auto balance check</li>
    <li>Cash &amp; bank; cheque / PDC; mode-of-payment control</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">Receivables &amp; Payables</td><td><ul>
    <li>Customer &amp; supplier ledgers; AR / AP aging (30 / 60 / 90)</li>
    <li>Outstanding tracking &amp; statements</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">General Ledger &amp; Financials</td><td><ul>
    <li>Chart of accounts &amp; account groups; trial balance</li>
    <li>Balance Sheet and Profit &amp; Loss</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">Inventory Costing &amp; Stock</td><td><ul>
    <li>Stock valuation &amp; COGS; item costing; purchase entries &amp; stock reports</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">Multi-Currency</td><td><ul>
    <li>Currency master &amp; conversion rates; foreign-currency totals</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr><td class="g">Reports &amp; Document Designer</td><td><ul>
    <li>Sales / purchase / financial reports, profit analysis &amp; day-book</li>
    <li>Custom invoice / voucher / cheque print designer</li></ul></td></tr>
</table>

<div class="sec">4.&nbsp; Pricing</div>
<table class="price">
  <tr><th>Description</th><th style="text-align:right;width:20%;">Amount (AED)</th><th style="text-align:right;width:14%;">VAT 5%</th><th style="text-align:right;width:20%;">Total (AED)</th></tr>
  <tr><td>BOS Property Management &amp; Accounts Software (one-time)</td><td class="num">15,000.00</td><td class="num">750.00</td><td class="num">15,750.00</td></tr>
  <tr class="total"><td>Total Contract Value</td><td class="num">15,000.00</td><td class="num">750.00</td><td class="num">15,750.00</td></tr>
</table>
<div class="note">All amounts in UAE Dirham (AED). VAT charged at 5%. This is a one-time software licence &amp; implementation fee &mdash; not a recurring subscription.</div>

<div class="sec">5.&nbsp; Payment Terms &amp; One-Month Trial</div>
<table class="price">
  <tr><th>Stage</th><th>When</th><th style="text-align:right;width:24%;">Amount (incl. VAT)</th></tr>
  <tr><td><b>1. Initial Payment</b> &mdash; installation, setup &amp; training</td><td>On installation (Day&nbsp;1 = <b>28th</b>)</td><td class="num">2,500 + VAT = <b>2,625.00</b></td></tr>
  <tr><td><b>2. One-Month Test &amp; Trial</b> &mdash; insert your real data &amp; start using it</td><td>Day 1 &rarr; Day 30</td><td class="num">&mdash;</td></tr>
  <tr><td><b>3. Balance</b> &mdash; payable only if you decide to purchase</td><td>End of trial</td><td class="num">12,500 + VAT = <b>13,125.00</b></td></tr>
</table>

<p style="margin-top:10px;"><b>How the initial 2,500 + VAT works:</b></p>
<ul class="terms">
  <li><span class="badge-y">IF YOU PURCHASE</span> the software after the trial &mdash; the <b>2,500 AED + VAT (2,625)</b> is <b>deducted from the main amount</b>. You pay only the balance <b>12,500 + VAT = 13,125 AED</b>, and the total stays <b>15,750 AED</b>.</li>
  <li><span class="badge-n">IF YOU DO NOT PURCHASE</span> &mdash; the <b>2,500 AED + VAT (2,625)</b> is retained as a <b>service charge towards software installation &amp; training expenses</b> incurred during the trial period.</li>
</ul>

<div class="note">
  <b>Trial advantage:</b> During the one-month test &amp; trial you get the fully working system &mdash; you can enter your properties, tenants, contracts and accounts and run your real operations. Whatever data you enter during the trial is retained when you purchase, so there is no re-work.
</div>

<div class="sec">6.&nbsp; What's Included</div>
<ul>
  <li>On-site / remote installation and configuration on Day 1 (28th).</li>
  <li>Setup of your company, users, roles, chart of accounts and property masters.</li>
  <li>Hands-on staff training during the trial period.</li>
  <li>Full Real-Estate (Property Management) and Accounts / Finance modules.</li>
  <li>One month of live test &amp; trial support with real data.</li>
</ul>

